column5: The jury is still out on the authenticity of this story, but it doesn't seem completely outside the realm of possibility: http://doubtfulnews.com/2013/09/entire-knife-found-in-salmon-hmm/
Thats pretty out there but i still think its true! Lol
Looks like it went in handle first.. that was my first question... seems plausible. Lol makes ya wonder what else they've found in fish bellies over the years.
I can't wait for the new line of lures that imitate filet knives.
